:"2019-06-17T02:50:46.000Z","msg":"[下一步]係時侯要求將陳同佳移交台灣受審,交波俾English蔡<br />\n<br />\n好處有以下幾點<br />\n1.令犯人得到應有既懲罰<br />\n2.打多林鄭一巴,證明逃犯條例係多9魚<br />\n3.助攻台灣反共勢力<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234536\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234536</a>"},{"pid":"80494a458ef8084372185b442b982e937bef954c","tid":1234120,"uid":6777,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"又比english 消費反送中 爭民意支持<br />\n老老豆豆，對台灣黎講除左口上威下，其實無咩實際幫助，因為本身台灣就係好完整既國家<br />\n<br />\n台灣最需要既係維持不表現狀爭取經濟民生發展，無錢係手仲講咩保衛家園<br />\n<br />\n只要唔損害主權，咩都係可以傾，而唔係下下撐到行純粹攞彩<br />\n<br />\n對於逃犯條例就一定係表態反對，係岩既，但過度消費既話，台灣人又會比民進黨用民族意識呢啲虛幻野撚多 4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1185492eec246ef39d505db54c3c502b85288b19","tid":1234120,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747f5f37989c5fa9a41cda33c8a437a01841c6af","tid":1234120,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"ENGLIGH靠呢戰拉返民意"},{"pid":"071e42c19e36a7f693783e47a54a3abac461c44c","tid":1234120,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62fbba4d67bd36b695a158aa8d7bc4bd3da06117","tid":1234120,"uid":39855,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"小英火力全開，香港已經示範左，冇民主，有錢又點。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"錢? 而家中共明搶香港納稅人D錢,香港人又做到咩?<br />\nD錢從來都唔係我地既"},{"pid":"8747cd0b6f332b10b6b7306b0cc0d9a0ba143a67","tid":1234120,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"071e42c19e36a7f693783e47a54a3abac461c44c","tid":1234120,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62fbba4d67bd36b695a158aa8d7bc4bd3da06117","tid":1234120,"uid":39855,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"小英火力全開，香港已經示範左，冇民主，有錢又點。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:02:35.000Z","msg":"錢? 而家中共明搶香港納稅人D錢,香港人又做到咩?<br />\nD錢從來都唔係我地既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"搶香港錢幫唔到貿易戰好多<br />\n<br />\n相反原本韓國瑜做總統後<br />\n中國可以不流血統一台灣<br />\n<br />\n會成為貿易戰的突破點<br />\n充公台積電<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b0ac45275039c06f08faed1a900822c5feb688","tid":1234120,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"蔡英文真係唔停咁左一巴右一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3537c7cfee3364a146357c373e0f01ea8c9618e6","tid":1234120,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55b0ac45275039c06f08faed1a900822c5feb688","tid":1234120,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"蔡英文真係唔停咁左一巴右一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}